VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT addLogger\s*\(\s*StdOutSqlLogger\s*\)|addLogger\s*\(\s*Slf4jSqlDebugLogger\s*\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:if.*debug|DEBUG|isDevelopment|isTest|\.debug
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Kotlin Exposed SQL loggers enabled without debug/development build gating.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for addLogger in Production Code Path.
